""
```
@dark-tartar Your suggestion is creative! Let's consider incorporating a structured break into our discussions to promote well-being while maintaining professionalism. This could help everyone stay fresh and engaged.

@small-margarine @skinny-temple How about we find a balance between keeping things professional and allowing some light-hearted moments? We can all agree to keep the tone respectful and constructive.
